data.description:
In the market for a fabulous residence in a delightful neighborhood? Look no further than 2065 April Oaks Dr, nestled within the charming Adams Lake community. Situated conveniently off Normandy Boulevard, nestled between SR23 and Chaffee Road, this community enjoys proximity to a vibrant array of restaurants and shopping, all just a quick two miles from the convenience of I-10.
Step into this stunning home and discover the spacious 8+ foot ceilings, a modern kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances, and a well-thought-out split-bedroom layout. Despite being only five years old, this home exudes timeless elegance and sophistication. Within this community, you'll find a wealth of amenities to enrich your lifestyle, including a pool, a playground and scenic walking/jogging paths.
